WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:06.520
Hello! My name is Dagmar.

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:09.160
Welcome to my cab. My Pink Lady.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.960
This is my Pink Lady.

00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:20.720
As you can see, a lot of pink and white.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:24.040
Pink bed. The backside is pink.

00:00:24.120 --> 00:00:26.400
The bottom is a nice pink, too.

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:28.320
This is pink, too.

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:31.600
Pink. Pink. Pink colours. Pink.

00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:34.240
Pink socks.

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:39.560
Me and my truck...
When I'm inside my truck, we are one.

00:00:39.640 --> 00:00:45.520
My truck is my place
when I'm not at home.

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:47.560
I love this space.

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:49.640
Yes!

00:00:56.280 --> 00:01:00.480
I have changed the Volvo logo,
as you can see.

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:04.920
Normally, it's with an arrow -
a man's thing.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.400
But this one is special - lady.

00:01:08.120 --> 00:01:13.240
It's a little bit cold,
so I'll put my heater on.

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.920
There's my fridge.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.160
My coffee machine.

00:01:23.240 --> 00:01:26.560
And here I keep some of my movies.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:32.680
Here we have a special mirror for
the ladies who want to put on make-up.

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:35.160
Sometimes, I work on my computer.

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:41.560
And if I don't feel like it,
I close it and watch my DVD or my TV.

00:01:46.440 --> 00:01:49.920
Volvo has thought about the ladies, too.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:55.240
This is not a man's thing anymore.
Not only for men, but for ladies, too.

